---
/**
 * StatsSection - About-us summary section for the homepage.
 * Displays company overview text alongside a 2x2 grid of key statistics.
 */
---

<section class="bg-cream py-16 lg:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
    <!-- Left column: text -->
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
      <span class="text-tibetan-red tracking-[0.2em] text-sm font-semibold uppercase">
        ABOUT US
      </span>
      <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-ink-blue leading-tight">
        扎根秘境卓尼
        <br />
        连接高原与世界
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-earth-brown leading-relaxed">
        藏宝宝扎根于甘南藏族自治州卓尼县，依托高原独特的自然资源与深厚的藏医药文化，致力于将雪域高原的珍贵药材与藏地好物带给更多人，连接高原秘境与广阔世界。
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a
          href="/about"
          class="inline-block border-2 border-tibetan-red text-tibetan-red px-6 py-3 rounded-md text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-tibetan-red hover:text-white"
        >
          了解更多 &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right column: 2x2 stat cards -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 lg:gap-6">
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg text-center shadow-sm">
        <p class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-tibetan-red">10万+</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-earth-brown">服务人口</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg text-center shadow-sm">
        <p class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-tibetan-red">136种</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-earth-brown">野生药材</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg text-center shadow-sm">
        <p class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-tibetan-red">8大</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-earth-brown">产品品类</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg text-center shadow-sm">
        <p class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-tibetan-red">5139</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-earth-brown">km² 服务区域</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
